Class Instrument

  • java.lang.Object
    • Instrument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Percussion, StringInstrument, Wind

    abstract class Instrument
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Instrument.java represents the instruments managed by the music department that is a superclass of Wind, StringInstrument, and Percussion.
